TopicTitle: Waiter, theres a _____________ in my soup!

Articles.Content:
Sir, may I remind you that you ordered electronic duck soup?

Waiter! There's a dead kerbal in my soup.

Well, Danny2462 IS the chef.

Waiter, there's Civ 5 complete pack in my soup!

You ordered the special soup. It comes with all dlcs! Oh yeah, here's your bill. *hands you a 500 dollar bill*

Waiter, there are earphones in my soup!

I thought you wanted "Rock Soup"

WAITOR! There is a Kraken biting Danny2462 in my soup!

Just fish 'em out.

Waiter, there's a stick figure webcomic in my soup!

You ordered the special soup. It comes with all dlcs! Oh yeah, here's your bill. *hands you a 500 dollar bill*

Well, I got it on a steam sale for 15$! ALL DLCS!

We though you wanted the "Comic Relief" soup.

Waitor! There is rocket fuel in my soup!

rocket fuel? I dont think it is... *takes a blow torch* if this lights up then it is.

WAITER!!! JEB IS SWIMING IS IN MY SOUP HIS IS BUILDING LIKE A ROCKET!!!!!

Uh oh. Quick, get him out of there before he... *Jeb lights the firework rocket* Ok, nope nope nope RUN! JUST RUN FOR YOUR LIFE!

Waiter, there's a space helmet in my soup.

Yeah.. That's yours

Waiter, Niel Armstrong is in my soup.

You should be happy if thats the case!

Waiter,A sock is in my soup!

Did you not order blue cheese soup?

waiter xannari ferrows is in my soup

Xan? Please get out of his soup!

Waiter, why is gibberish in my soup?

Seehum jar bushy garf.

Waiter, there is a suspicious hyperlink in my soup!

Oh, don't worry. Just click it, you'll win a free ipad too!

Waiter, there is he-man in my soup... He just won't stop singing...

Plug your ears.

Waiter, there's a copy of ET: The Videogame in my soup.

Quick! Kill it with fire!

Waiter, theres fire in my soup.

So? What of it?

Water, there's an LV-N Atomic Rocket Motor in my soup!

Ssh! Keep quiet, this thing is supposed to land on the black market...

Waiter, there is no soup in my soup.

That's the low calorie healthy option Sir, finest quality water made with no added ingredients.

Waiterrr, theresh alcololol in my shoupp.!!

You ordered the alcaholic version! replaces all water with scotch!

Waaaaaiiiituuuurrrrr! there's a turd in my soup!

I thought you ordered "GOD DANG IT! Fine, get me your crappiest soup" soup.

WAITERRRRRRRRRRRRRR! There is a Nassault in my soup!

He's filming an underwater scene.

Waiter, there's a being of pure energy inside my soup.

He has a plasma gun.

and a UFO.

Well you did ask for a surprising new flavour.

Waiter, there's a Martian in my soup.

It's a bean!

Waiter, there's Antvenom in my soup.

No, those are Captain grade sparkelez.

(Hope I got that reference correct)

Waiter, I have kerosene in my soup!
